name: A Dreaming Grape
description:
This shirt was designed to compliment the Jordan Grape 5's. The design is a parody of the Bathing Ape brand. It features Sheepy, the Tecknicolor mascot and the text reads "A Dreaming Grape".

The shirt is 100% 4.5 cotton and was printing in the US.

name: Looney Dreams
description:
This shirt was designed as a compliment to the Jordan 8 Hare or Bugs Bunny's. It features the Sheepy, the Tecknicolor mascot redesigned to resemble Bugs Bunny and the test reads "Looney Dreams".

The shirt is 100% 4.5 Cotton and the design is printed in the US.

name: Breezy Hampton X Tecknicolor Bracelet
description: This piece is a design collaboration with Breezy Hampton a new accessories brand. It makes the perfect valentines day gift. Each bracelet is carefully hand crafted here in the US. Wrist Measurement (inches) Use measuring tape, wrap it completely around your wrist in a comfortable fashion where the bracelet is to be worn. Medium - 7 to 8 1/2 Large - 9 to 10

name: Bred Dreamers Market
description: PYOP is a Cyber Monday sale that allows you to choose your own price for the item of your choice. I will ONLY accept offers over $10 anything less than that will not receive a response. To make an offer: - Email tecknicolorsales@gmail.com - Put the name of the shirt in the subject line. - Let me know the size and the offer in the body If you're offer is accepted, you will receive a Paypal invoice for said amount. Shipping will begin starting next week, December 2nd SALES ARE 1st COME 1st SERVE, WHILE SUPPLIES LAST. This shirt was designed to compliment the Retro Jordan 11's in Black in Red. They are often referred to as the Bred's. So the design is of the Tecknicolor Dreamers Market which is selling BRED at an amazing 11 cents a loaf, BAKED FRESH DAILY. EDIT: The 11 cents has been replaced with the word SALE in order to allow the shirt to match all BRED Jordans. The shirt is screen printed in USA on 100% cotton, 4.5 t-shirt.

name: All Gold Every Dream [white]
description:
This shirt was designed to compliment the "Gold Medal" Pack

Nike Zoom KD IV “Gold”, Nike LeBron X - Sports Pack "USA", Nike Zoom Kobe VII "Gold", and Nike Hyperdunk "Gold".

The design takes the now famous Jay-Z line "All Black Everything" and puts a Tecknicolor Dream Team spin on it, with the text reading ALL GOLD EVERY DREAM written in metallic gold. It also features Tecknicolor sheep cutout logos as the Olympic rings in red, navy and silver.

The design is screen printed on 4.5 100% cotton t-shirts.

name: All Gold Every Dream [SOLD OUT]
description:
This shirt was designed to compliment the many Olympic themed sneaker that were released in the month of July:

Air Force 180, Air Max More Uptempo, Huarache 2K4, Nike Shox BB4, Air Force 1 High, Retro Jordan 6 and Retro Jordan 7

The design takes the now famous Jay-Z line "All Black Everything" and puts a Tecknicolor Dream Team spin on it, with the text reading ALL GOLD EVERY DREAM written in metallic gold. It also features Tecknicolor sheep cutout logos as the olympic rings in red, white and silver.

The design is screen printed on 4.5 100% cotton t-shirts.

name: Stacks & Stripes
description:
This shirt was designed to compliment the Retro Olympic Jordan VI's.

The design is consists of red shoe boxes aligned in into stacks that appear as the stripes on the American flag. The shirt as well as the sneaker are releasing just as we begin to go into the 2012 Olympic Games. This shirt is the perfect way to show you support for team USA.

Printed on 4.5 100% Cotton t-shirt

name: Just Blue It
description:
This shirt was designed to compliment the Retro Jordan 4's in the Military Blue color way. 

It's a text focused design that read's "Just Blue It", with the word blue having a double meaning (blue/blew). It features a mini cannon that appears to be shooting the Tecknicolor sheep mascot across the tee, wearing a Camo helmet. The concept is has military theme with the cannon and the sheep represents us shooting towards our dreams.

All shirts are printed on Anvil 100% Cotton 4.5oz. T-shirts

name: Elite Dreams (South Beach)
description:
The design is simple. It's a slogan that encourages all of us dreamers to dream big and without limitations. The text reads "Dream Like An Elitest".

The word Elitest is spelled with an E rather than an I to emphasize the parody on the logo from well known street wear brand Fatlace, which reads Illest and is a parody of the golf company's logo, Titleist.

This shirt was created to compliment the Nike Lebron 9 PS Elite "South Beaches".

name: KREAM Anonymous: 12 Steps
description:
The shirt was designed to compliment the Jordan "Playoff" 12's

The design features a recovering KREAM-a-holic Monster, who resembles another monster that lives on Sesame Street and also has a addiction to cookies (yet he never gains weight).His goal is help all those with sneaker addictions through his 12 step program.

If you want join his group just purchase this tee and you too can be a part of KREAM Anonymous.

name: Power of Four
description:
This tee was designed to compliment the Retro Jordan 4's in white and cement.

The design was inspired by the comic/movie Thor. The hammer handle says "Whoever wears this shirt, if he be worthy, shall posses the power of".... Which is similar to the message on Thor's hammer.

name: Concord Cola
description:
This shirt was designed to compliment the Retro Jordan 11's in concord and white.

The Coke inspired design is based on a limited edition bottle designed by Chanel's head designer, Karl Lagerfeld. It features the Tecknicolor Sheep mascot as as waiter carrying "Concord Cola" in a X shaped ice bucket with an I shaped champagne fluke. The ice is the same color as the soles of the Concords the waiter is wearing.

The text on the shirt says "Concord Wishes and Tecknicolor Dreams"

name: Three's Tees Package
description:
This package includes all three colors of The Tecknicolor Circus: Greatest Show on Mars [White, True Blue, Black] .

This shirt was created to compliment the Jordan 3's.

The design inspiration in based on a well known elephant that was able to fly because of his very large ears and became a popular act at the circus. This design was also inspired by the line (re-written in less offensive stereotypical language) "I've seen about everything when I see an elephant fly."

The design is screen printed on 100% cotton 4.5 Anvil t-shirts.

Please specify which three sizes you want when paying if you're mixing sizes.
